column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, pz.z as photoredshift, petroR5#_r, GN.distance, SM.logMass FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid JOIN PhotoZ AS pz ON pz.objid = p.objid JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, +#, #) AS GN ON p.objID = GN.objID JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust AS SM ON SM.specObjID = p.objID WHERE s.class = GALAXY
